124:    * The payment on default.
125:    * <p>
126:    * Whether the accrued premium is paid in the event of a default.
127:    * <p>
128:    * When building, this will default to 'AccruedPremium'.
129:    */
130:   @PropertyDefinition(validate = "notNull")
131:   private final PaymentOnDefault paymentOnDefault;
